rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">Direktori Public</h2><p id=\"3219\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Setelah selesai instalasi Laravel, kita bisa mengkonfigurasikan web server ducument / web root ke direktori&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">public</span>. File&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">index.php&nbsp;</span>yang ada di folder public ini adalah file php yang digunakan untuk menerima semua request yang masuk ke website kita. Kita bisa lihat dan pelajari apa saja yang ada pada file index.php seperti&nbsp;<em class=\"kg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">require autoload.php</em>&nbsp;pada folder vendor.</p><h2 id=\"1e71\" class=\"jk ih ca as ar bs ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.72em 0px -0.31em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">File Konfigurasi</h2><p id=\"ac98\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Semua konfigurasi yang ada pada framework Laravel disimpan pada direktori&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">config.</span></p><h2 id=\"615a\" class=\"jk ih ca as ar bs ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.72em 0px -0.31em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">Direktori Permissions</h2><p id=\"8d71\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Setelah install Laravel, pastikan kita konfigurasi permission. Direktori seperti&nbsp;<em class=\"kg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">storage</em>&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<em class=\"kg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">bootstrap/cache&nbsp;</em>harus dalam keadaan&nbsp;<em class=\"kg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">writable&nbsp;</em>atau dapat diakses oleh web server. Berikut perintah yang digunakan pada OS unix.</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"f883\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">sudo chgrp -R www-data storage bootstrap/cache<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">sudo chmod -R ug+rwx storage bootstrap/cache</span></pre><p id=\"c6e4\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp hq ib hr hs ic ht hu id hv hw ie hx hy if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Jika masih muncul error bisa dengan perintah pamungkas berikut</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"4c0f\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">sudo chmod -R 777 bootstrap/cache<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">sudo chmod -R 777</span></pre><h2 id=\"8e45\" class=\"jk ih ca as ar bs ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.72em 0px -0.31em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">.Env</h2><p id=\"a4f5\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Kumpulan variable konfigurasi yang dibutuhkan di file config atau lainnya. untuk load variable tersebut bisa menggunakan function env(‘nama-key’). Library yang laravel gunakan ialah&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/vlucas/phpdotenv\" class=\"ct fs je jf jg jh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(41, 41, 41, 1)\\&quot; ></line></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">vlucas/phpdotenv</a>.</p><h2 id=\"597d\" class=\"jk ih ca as ar bs ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.72em 0px -0.31em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">Application Key</h2><p id=\"10c7\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Langkah yang tidak boleh terlewatkan ialah set application key menggunakan random string. Jika kita menginstall menggunakan composer, key ini sudah dibuatkan dengan menggunakan perintah&nbsp;<a href=\"http://twitter.com/php\" class=\"ct fs je jf jg jh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(41, 41, 41, 1)\\&quot; ></line></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\"><span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">@php</span></a><span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;artisan key:generate,&nbsp;</span>bisa kita lihat di file composer.json didalam project bagian array&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">scripts</span>&nbsp;yang berada paling bawah. String key ini dibuat pada file .env. Jika file .env belum tersedia bisa mengcopy dari file .env.example dan jalankan perintah</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"25ed\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">php artisan key:generate</span></pre><p id=\"e5f8\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp hq ib hr hs ic ht hu id hv hw ie hx hy if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">maka hasilnya bisa dilihat di file .env</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"19d4\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">APP_NAME=Laravel<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">APP_ENV=local<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">APP_KEY=base64:WIcGd9yjV2jmJW6RHJOQ4ober6leVvD0RPr9ccbXl0g=<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">APP_DEBUG=true<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">APP_URL=<a href=\"http://localhost/\" class=\"ct fs je jf jg jh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(41, 41, 41, 1)\\&quot; ></line></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">http://localhost</a></span></pre><p id=\"a4f6\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp hq ib hr hs ic ht hu id hv hw ie hx hy if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">untuk lokasi confignya berada di folder&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">config/app.php&nbsp;</span>dengan nama ‘key’</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"0587\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">/*<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — <br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | Encryption Key<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — — <br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> |<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | This key is used by the Illuminate encrypter service and should be set<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | to a random, 32 character string, otherwise these encrypted strings<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> | will not be safe. Please do this before deploying an application!<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> |<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> */</span><span id=\"cee7\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jp jq jr js jt jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 1.91em;\">‘key’ =&gt; env(‘APP_KEY’),</span><span id=\"d023\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jp jq jr js jt jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 1.91em;\">‘cipher’ =&gt; ‘AES-256-CBC’,</span></pre><h2 id=\"0d59\" class=\"jk ih ca as ar bs ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.72em 0px -0.31em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-size: 26px;\">Database Konfigurasi</h2><p id=\"6c20\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp ir ib hr is ic ht it id hv iu ie hx iv if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">Untuk konfigurasi database kita bisa edit melalui file .env. Pada kali ini saya kasih contoh konfigurasi untuk database mysql, kita bisa mengisi isian berikut ini, disesuaikan dengan nama database, username dan password mysql:</p><pre class=\"go gp gq gr gs ji jj cg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 20px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><span id=\"a24f\" class=\"jk ih ca as jl b ex jm jn r jo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">DB_CONNECTION=mysql<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">DB_HOST=127.0.0.1<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">DB_PORT=3306<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">DB_DATABASE=laravel<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">DB_USERNAME=root<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">DB_PASSWORD=</span></pre><p id=\"bb44\" class=\"hm ia ca as ho b hp hq ib hr hs ic ht hu id hv hw ie hx hy if hz dn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\">untuk lokasi config database mysql berada di folder&nbsp;<span class=\"ho kf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">config/database.php.</span></p></div></div>', 'articles/4Mb23LIrzx8Xkw2IUT96Mrf7wCbKdnUUdOYPgD6W.jpeg', 5, '2020-06-14 07:31:15', '2020-06-15 05:53:44'),
